################################################################################
#  MirageVC - A Model-View-Controller framework for PHP
################################################################################

INSTALLATION

________________________________________________________________________________
-  Method 1:  Global Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy the MirageVC directory to the directory specified in your php_includes
directory (as defined in php.ini) and include it implicitly.

  - or - 

Add the MirageVC directory to php_includes in php.ini and include it implicitly.

EG.
require_once( 'MirageVC.php' ) ;





________________________________________________________________________________
-  Method 2:   Local Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add the MirageVC directory somewhere within your application's root dir and 
include it directly.

EG.
require_once( './lib/MirageVC/MirageVC.php' ) ;

